Quote:  Mountain Trout or Giant Galaxias <i>Galaxias argenteus</i> (Gmelin) (Syn. <i>G. alepidotus</i> Bloch and Schneider, <i>G. forsteri</i> Cuv. and Val. <i>G. grandis</i> Clarke, preocc., and <i>G. kokopu</i> Clarke)
Notes:  1955 Whitley Namelist in 1956 Graham NZ Fishes 399

